race.description: Jawa Off Road Campers Maiden Handicap
race.comment: DIALIDAE (2) has been just behind the placegetters in town of late and will appreciate the drop back in company here. Will be cherry-ripe now fourth-up from the spell and is sure to be right there when the judge calls a halt. CARBONARA (1) is knocking on the door of a maiden victory with runner-up finishes in three of her past four outings. Only needs some luck from the wide draw to be playing a major role in the outcome. ISLA DELILAH (4) is at the races for the first time but is sure to be well-educated from the Munce barn. Monitor market activity. REEVACITY (8) was okay at Ipswich on debut and will have derived a stack of benefit from that race day experience. One for the multiples. HEART 'N' POWER (12) next best from the favourable draw.
